Rafael Nadal beat Nicolas Almagro 6-3 6-1 at the Barcelona Open on Wednesday . 
  The world No 4 is looking for his ninth career title on the Catalan clay court . 
  Nadal was watched by Barcelona forward Neymar in the crowd . 
  The Spaniard will play Fabio Fognini or Andrey Rublev in the third round . 
 